Text: Re Financial Trading Issues in BrazilSara I did receive your message Next week looks like a hectic one I will then be in New York from Sept through Thus your last suggested dates Sept seems to be the most appropriate I look forward to hearing from you Best regards Jos Emilio Sara Shackleton pm Although I am still waiting for another Brazilian visa I would like to pose several potential dates to meet with you regarding Enron North America Corp trading issues I am presently considering several time periods September Obviously I can be available at any time during the month of Septermber as well as future months But I would like to get started as soon as possible If you could kindly email or call me I can elaborate further Thank you Sara
